about.summary: Testing, monitoring and dating structural changes in (linear) regression models. strucchange features tests/methods from the generalized fluctuation test framework as well as from the F test (Chow test) framework. This includes methods to fit, plot and test fluctuation processes (e.g., CUSUM, MOSUM, recursive/moving estimates) and F statistics, respectively. It is possible to monitor incoming data online using fluctuation processes. Finally, the breakpoints in regression models with structural changes can be estimated together with confidence intervals. Emphasis is always given to methods for visualizing the data.

name: r-strucchange
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = '1.5-1' %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-strucchange
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  fn: strucchange_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/strucchange_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/strucchange/strucchange_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 740e2e20477b9fceeef767ae1002adc5ec397cb0f7daba5289a2c23b0dddaf31

build:
  noarch: generic
  merge_build_host: True  # [win]
  number: 1002
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{posix}}zip               # [win]
  host:
    - r-base
    - r-sandwich
    - r-zoo
  run:
    - r-base
    - r-sandwich
    - r-zoo

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('strucchange')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('strucchange')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: https://CRAN.R-project.org/package=strucchange
  license: GPL-2 | GPL-3
  summary: Testing, monitoring and dating structural changes in (linear) regression models. strucchange
    features tests/methods from the generalized fluctuation test framework as well as
    from the F test (Chow test) framework. This includes methods to fit, plot and test
    fluctuation processes (e.g., CUSUM, MOSUM, recursive/moving estimates) and F statistics,
    respectively. It is possible to monitor incoming data online using fluctuation processes.
    Finally, the breakpoints in regression models with structural changes can be estimated
    together with confidence intervals. Emphasis is always given to methods for visualizing
    the data.
  license_family: GPL3
  license_file: '{{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/GPL-3'

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
    - johanneskoester
    - bgruening
    - daler
    - jdblischak
    - cbrueffer
    - dbast
